{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"张萌萌","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-07","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98WwquGlBAMm2Ria0y4TSM0NXjDJpd644Fu5bHnVeNqSI7BCicplwsyptjam2BARefsz3s9DibKm6PghdfLZm64tWoI/0","content":"一  反向提问\n1.特朗普若支持台湾，大陆为什么不首先惩罚美国，而是台湾？\n2.特朗普若支持台湾，大陆为什么不同时惩罚台湾和美国？\n3.特朗普若支持台湾，大陆为什么要惩罚？\n二 思考\n1.中国的目的是收复台湾，不使台湾独立出去，而不是与美国发生冲突。惩罚台湾，一方面是表明立场，台湾是中华人民共和国不可分割的一部分，不要打独立的主意；另一方面，我推测，与惩罚美国相比，惩罚台湾付出的代价要小。\n2.同时惩罚，对中国的自身经济也会影响很大，找准重点突破才是上策。\n","voteCount":2,"commentCount":0,"submitId":518,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1486452597000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"浥尘","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-06","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoNL7EDTAve1O74gANzM4RwsvL08Gm6ViarRN6kNic8JzthiapekyDe9cgpm8wiat4QEF78Kvmj4YZ27Y/0","content":"1特普朗若支持台湾，大陆若不惩罚台湾而首先惩罚美国会怎么样\n2特普朗若不支持台湾，大陆会不会奖励台湾\n3若美国以外的其他国家支持台湾，大陆会首先惩罚台湾吗\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":500,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1486375492000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"\uD83D\uDD06","submitUpdateTime":"2017-01-26","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AywPmsfj50SsWwLgXs2ESDQGlVDnBLKvNVxx6ia89su8exV77LyYjFNLOeMQpIDk7G1Yc04FXzkbhZ/0","content":"特朗普不支持台湾会怎样？\n\n特朗普支持台湾，大陆可能首先惩罚美国而非台湾","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":407,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1485403514000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"上善若水","submitUpdateTime":"2017-01-22","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQDZRnEAypu396mq2FzNVSFDcMGHy6ibvCRicufUpu1mvNTzx40BWldtBSibjktrlVcmEkPgCDQKw88Y/0","content":"1、特朗普若支持台湾，大陆会不会先惩罚美国而不是台湾？如果先惩罚美国，会采取怎么样的方式惩罚？对美国和中国人们带来哪些影响？其实我想问特朗普若支持台湾，支持的是什么？是台独么？\n2、特朗普若不支持台湾，大陆会对美国和台湾各采取什么样的行动呢？\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":364,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1485091953000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"彭兄","submitUpdateTime":"2017-01-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XrFctaWMO6Hek8JfFDOtEWYnA1pDX3hqjFlmjKDCFj3jID1iaMsXedtNka7iaBAcWnQiaZCCzKlMFyQ/0","content":"特朗普若支持台湾，大陆首先惩罚美国而不是台湾会怎样？\n世界大战，一起玩完，两败俱伤。因此绝对不敢先打美国。\n\n如果美国媒体称，特朗普不支持台湾，会怎样？\n特朗普会以为美国媒体向自己投怀送抱了，不是希拉里的人了。\n大陆会放松警惕，以为特朗普不再逗比，可以好好聊聊了。\n\n\n\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":331,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1484971326000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Evelyn","submitUpdateTime":"2017-01-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6ZaLoY2RXU5FfnPYQicNKvU8piclQWvZStXH9QBFyxhlvc0JG22elM8ickAaGywcjhbN8GfGA1icDZvLMuglIsEHTrt/0","content":"占坑，待回答","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":311,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1484826568000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Cindy.C","submitUpdateTime":"2017-01-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaEJkkL8Ou2K0edGIQdDlb7icTgXnpsHT9DCGEn1hIq5S4Gz3X4O0bpgfzlDf3iaV4O9ePniaNuaymibKgA/0","content":"特朗普若不支持台湾，美国媒体会怎么声称？\n特朗普若支持台湾，其他媒体会怎么声称？\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":230,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1484722046000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"何亮","submitUpdateTime":"2017-01-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/Q3auHgzwzM79KmGmpAH0BiaocqYvtpZUyIQPHh7WQagrCrOd0LsKUBLicRzkTCaVg1y3ykLNAibNNqKEH7h4eALKw/0","content":"正向提问：特朗普若支持台湾，为什么大陆首先惩罚台湾而不是美国？》\n反向提问：特朗普若支持台湾，为什么大陆不是首先惩罚美国？\n          特朗普若支持台湾，大陆首先惩罚美国将会怎样？\n发现：台湾问题是中美关系的核心，具有高度的敏感性，是否坚持一个中国政策和中美三个联合公报原则，是否慎重妥善处理涉台问题，将关系到中美关系大局是否受到严重干扰和损害。\n思考：通过此问题可以看出中国的外交和军事策略，惩罚台湾，减损台湾对美国的价值，而不是直指美国，毕竟目前两国的正面交战所造成的影响甚大。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":226,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1484715686000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Elisa","submitUpdateTime":"2017-01-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLDs2amzGE0Hvu4bUsNSut5wTQA43MAS653Pics7Fh5ZTXaK0uv0mwzt5iaJnQcgeumUJ1MTnwlIibrNRhzefk4v9VT5KTgUPG7x9A/0","content":"1,特朗普为什么要支持台湾？\n2,特朗普若支持台湾，为什么是大陆要惩罚台湾而不是其它国家，如日本？\n3,特朗普若支持台湾，为什么大陆首先惩罚不是美国而是台湾？\n4,特朗普若不支持台湾，大陆还会惩罚台湾吗？\n\n大陆与台湾的关系亲密，一旦关系破灭，台湾答应了美国的支持，就相当于承认了台湾独立事件，这是大陆人民所不认同的行为。首先惩罚台湾是名正言顺的国土安全的内部问题，并没有要上升到国际层面，需要和美国战斗。\n特朗普若支持台湾，表达了他的政治立场。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":208,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1484664023000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"/去 游泳","submitUpdateTime":"2017-01-16","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6ZaLoY2RXU5FcKx3nba4RDshES1lCD7tLNJqFfQ5zbHPtRXhjOE04TggHW5Aky49dUE2oSa0OXiaW9AYHBjmlVv9/0","content":"暂时还没有思考。\n不过圈外第三个思考题给出了一些方向，可以用反向问题法来开拓思路。\n对今天的思考。\n原问句：如果特朗普支持台湾，大陆首先会惩罚台湾\n反向：如果特朗普支持其他国家，大陆会惩罚台湾吗？\n反向：如果特朗普支持台湾，大陆会惩罚其他国家吗？\n反向：如果特朗普支持台湾，其他国家会惩罚台湾吗？\n\n以上问题得到的线索就是，美国、大陆、台湾三个地区的政治关系很微妙。美国对台湾的支持会影响大陆和台湾的关系。同时也反映美国对大陆的政治立场。如果将台湾换做其他国家。大陆不会有这样的反应。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":55,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1484558539000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]}],"highlightList":[],"end":true},"code":200}
